{"tid":1716203,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"其實跨欄真係好難，特別係個人笨重同起夜晚","createTime":"2019-11-13T09:38:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T10:11:36.000Z","uid":26041,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"385ba9202e2e1c3cdcba2a16ea1fdac82963b089","tid":1716203,"uid":26041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T09:38:20.000Z","msg":"最近想做多d運動操fit自己，等陸運會都有一技之長。於是放學後就綁條繩起屋企花園圍欄練習跨欄，一練就練到半夜，發現一唔夠光就好容易叉錯腳，而且升到中腰位就好容易仆親。不過練咗幾個月個人輕咗就容易好多，但如果無練過或者太重既絲巴就唔好試。但試過跨欄包你愛上佢！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n各位巴絲有冇學跨欄既好方法？<br />\n<br />\n利申：屋企好大，可以起花園練跨欄"},{"pid":"9434d80fa0fcfd5f2d5828da8631b4510b543227","tid":1716203,"uid":26041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T09:38:27.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"038689f8e652a1da51b92a3565f425e6aff70fe7","tid":1716203,"uid":26041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T09:38:37.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"49abdbf6afe1fe78eb46be1e0639726f11861431","tid":1716203,"uid":26041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T09:38:47.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"96ffa0461599eeb43c0803344c523d0bcf59b715","tid":1716203,"uid":26041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T09:38:59.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"fc3f9644f174d169493adcbcc09eee03e5f21330","tid":1716203,"uid":26041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T09:39:17.000Z","msg":"5/10"},{"pid":"b2704cbb20a7020d8d84ffd6ba10e06cce8a29cc","tid":1716203,"uid":140218,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T09:40:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=F3f1NhFzW9w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DF3f1NhFzW9w&d=eC9RRsiBNQJpYHZqEQI0Qhzw8eMAegQd4vHbNIzLZr4%3D&h=3ebf439d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=F3f1NhFzW9w</a><br />